name: GORILLA DELUXE BACKPACK
description:
The Gorilla Deluxe Backpack is the first of its kind. It features an all over fur exterior, and a gorilla face that will undoubtedly stop passers by. The Gorilla Deluxe Backpack is the ultimate fashion accessory, especially for those looking for that extra something to stand out from the crowd.

PRODUCT DETAILS:
Hidden large back compartment
Velour laptop sleeve
Padded tablet sleeve
Hidden stash
Four mesh-velcro accessory compartments
Padding on back for added support
Adjustable straps for custom sizing
Durable 900d Water-Resistant Fabric
Custom reinforced SBS Zippers and shoulder straps
Dimensions: 12’’ x 18’’ x 16’’

Instagram: latifsattar345
